{"tid":729474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"☭小米☭同股不同權   不符納入 MSCI 指數資格","createTime":"2018-07-04T14:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T17:10:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8637c1d88b76bdaf7df76e1ada9c6e88e4098f7c","tid":729474,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180704/large/1530694648_fd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180704%2Flarge%2F1530694648_fd0c.jpg&h=a37e2ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n☭小米☭獲眾多投資者捧場<br />\n<br />\nMSCI表示，☭小米☭不符合納入MSCI指數的資格，原因是其不平等投票架構。☭小米☭1股A股可獲10票投票權，但每股B股僅獲1票投票權。<br />\n<br />\n另外，☭小米☭於7月9日上市，港交所表示，相關期貨及期權將於同日推出。"},{"pid":"ca0efea5538b8c582facb945531c9bb2288aeca8","tid":729474,"uid":31762,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"李小家： MSCI落後，將被邊緣化。"},{"pid":"91ca46f43ad2614768c7300efe8ed5544e48cffe","tid":729474,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"個股價唔係話淨係meet到個最低預算咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/xiaomi-prices-hong-kong-ipo-at-bottom-of-target-range-1530250198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fxiaomi-prices-hong-kong-ipo-at-bottom-of-target-range-1530250198&d=ZcOiAZcDZ2f5NvGWbb8lmAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=89d40f07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/xiaomi-prices-hong-kong-ipo-at-bottom-of-target-range-1530250198</a>"},{"pid":"5db4fd5e58e2b82979813d4dbff759839bfca3bb","tid":729474,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"第一日就有Put輪玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77600b064c299e667d54b08761ad051460ed9971","tid":729474,"uid":7